data.title: NAE An and Amide CB1 Library
data.meta_description: NAE An and Amide CB1 Library - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides references for several papers and studies related to cannabinoids and endocannabinoid systems. It lists over 50 individual references published between 1994 and 2004 on topics including cannabinoid receptor biology, endocannabinoid signaling, effects of cannabinoids on various systems and tissues in the body, and therapeutic potential of cannabinoids. The references cover research in animal models and human studies.
